%BOM---------------------
Date:8/24/2004 1:37:56 PM
From:MCsweet
Oil futures,

Jurgis, yes the market believes oil will drop.

I think there might be a risk premium in oil futures so the futures price may
not quite be the expected spot price (i.e., investors are rewarded for the risk
of owning crude oil for future delivery so the futures price may be slightly
below the expected future spot price), but the futures prices would be my best
guess for where the market thinks oil is going.

MC
