%BOM---------------------
Date:8/25/2004 11:46:30 AM
From:MCsweet
Covered calls to hedge ALD,

Selling covered calls on ALD make be a good, profitable strategy, but I'm not
sure whether it hedges you well in this instance. If the short sellers are
right about Ponzi schemes or financial irregularity, you would lose a lot of
money on the long side, far outstripping the premium you make from selling the
call.

By the way, I don't know whether the stock is a buy or a sell or whether
selling covered calls on this is good or bad. Just making a general comment on
risk.

MC
